       A time-travel experiment in which a robot probe is sent from        Уь
       the year 2073 to the year 1973 goes terribly wrong thrusting        Уь
       one of the project scientists, a man named Nicholas Sinclair        Уь
       into a plague ravaged alternate time-line whose war weary           Уь
       inhabitants are locked in a constant battle with killer robots      Уь
       which are automatically being sent there from Sinclair's lab.       Уь
       To escape this situation, Sinclair must find a similar time         Уь
       machine in this alternate world and prevent the disaster from       Уь
       ever happening.                                                     Уь
